<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='216:243'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-1a' );" name="004-1a" class="pb">[004-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='243:250'>儀禮卷第四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='250:265'>鄕飮酒禮第四　儀禮　鄭氏注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='265:290'>鄕飮酒之禮主人就先生而謀賔介<span class='krp-note'>主人謂/諸侯之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='290:329'><span class='krp-note'>鄕大夫也先生鄕中致仕者賔介處士賢者/周禮大司徒之職以鄕三物教萬民而賔興</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='329:368'><span class='krp-note'>之一曰六德知仁聖義忠和二曰六行孝友/睦姻任恤三曰六藝禮樂射御書數鄕大夫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='368:407'><span class='krp-note'>以正月之吉受法于司徒退而頒之于其鄕/吏使各以教其所治以考其德行察其道藝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='407:446'><span class='krp-note'>及三年大比而興賢者能者鄕老及鄕大夫/帥其吏與其衆寡以禮禮賔之厥明獻賢能</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='446:485'><span class='krp-note'>之書於王是禮乃三年正月而一行也諸侯/之鄕大夫貢士於其君蓋如此云古者年七</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='485:512'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-1b' );" name="004-1b" class="pb">[004-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='512:551'><span class='krp-note'>十而致仕老於鄕里大夫名曰父師士名曰/少師而敎學焉恒知鄕人之賢者是以大夫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='551:590'><span class='krp-note'>就而謀之賢者爲賔其次爲介又其次爲衆/賔而與之飮酒是亦將獻之以禮禮賔之也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='590:629'><span class='krp-note'>今郡國十月行此飮酒禮以黨正毎歲邦索/鬼神而祭祀則以禮屬民而飮酒于序以正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='629:668'><span class='krp-note'>齒位之說然此篇無正齒位之事焉凡鄉黨/飮酒必於民聚之時欲其見化知尚賢尊長</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='668:698'><span class='krp-note'>也孟子曰天下有逹/尊三爵也德也齒也</span>主人戒賔賔拜辱主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='698:721'>荅拜乃請賔賔禮辭許主人再拜賔荅拜<span class='krp-note'>戒/警</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='721:759'><span class='krp-note'>也告也拜辱出拜其自屈辱至巳門也請/告以其所爲來之事不固辭者素所有志</span>主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='759:791'>人退賔拜辱<span class='krp-note'>退猶去也去又拜/辱者以送謝之</span>介亦如之<span class='krp-note'>如/戒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='791:818'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-2a' );" name="004-2a" class="pb">[004-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='818:854'><span class='krp-note'>賔/也</span>乃席賔主人介<span class='krp-note'>席敷席也夙興往戒歸而/敷席賔席牖前南靣主人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='854:887'><span class='krp-note'>席阼階上西靣介/席西階上東靣</span>衆賔之席皆不屬焉<span class='krp-note'>席衆/賔於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='887:918'><span class='krp-note'>賔席之西不屬者不相續/也皆獨坐明其德各特</span>尊兩壺于房戸間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='918:937'>斯禁有玄酒在西設篚于禁南東肆加二勺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='937:967'>于兩壺<span class='krp-note'>斯禁禁切地無足者玄/酒在西上也肆陳也</span>設洗于阼階</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='967:986'>東南南北以堂深東西當東榮水在洗東篚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='986:1016'>在洗西南肆<span class='krp-note'>榮屋/翼</span>羮定<span class='krp-note'>肉謂之羮/定猶孰也</span>主人速賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1016:1041'>賔拜辱主人荅拜還賔拜辱<span class='krp-note'>速召也/還猶退</span>介亦如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1041:1068'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-2b' );" name="004-2b" class="pb">[004-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1068:1102'>之<span class='krp-note'>如賔/速也</span>賔及衆賔皆從之<span class='krp-note'>從猶隨也言及衆/賔介亦在其中矣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1102:1121'>主人一相迎于門外再拜賔賔荅拜拜介介</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1121:1157'>荅拜<span class='krp-note'>相主人之吏/擯賛傳命者</span>揖衆賔<span class='krp-note'>差益卑也拜介揖/衆賔皆西南靣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1157:1184'>主人揖先入<span class='krp-note'>揖揖賔也先/入門而西面</span>賔厭介入門左介</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1184:1211'>厭衆賔入衆賔皆入門左北上<span class='krp-note'>皆入門西東/靣賔之屬相</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1211:1247'><span class='krp-note'>厭變於主人也推手曰揖引手曰厭/今文皆作揖又曰衆賔皆入左無門</span>主人與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1247:1266'>賔三揖至于階三讓主人升賔升主人阼階</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1266:1285'>上當楣北靣再拜賔西階上當楣北靣荅拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1285:1312'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-3a' );" name="004-3a" class="pb">[004-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1312:1346'><span class='krp-note'>三揖者將進揖當陳揖當碑揖楣/前梁也復拜拜賔至此堂尊之</span>主人坐取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1346:1375'>爵于篚降洗<span class='krp-note'>將獻/賔也</span>賔降<span class='krp-note'>從主/人也</span>主人坐奠爵于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1375:1411'>階前辭<span class='krp-note'>重以巳事煩賔也事/同曰讓事異曰辭</span>賔對<span class='krp-note'>對荅也賔/主之辭未</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1411:1432'><span class='krp-note'>聞</span>主人坐取爵興適洗南靣坐奠爵于篚下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1432:1464'>盥洗<span class='krp-note'>巳盥乃洗爵致絜/敬也今文無奠</span>賔進東北靣辭洗<span class='krp-note'>必/進</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1464:1488'><span class='krp-note'>東行/示情</span>主人坐奠爵于篚興對賔復位當西序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1488:1515'>東靣<span class='krp-note'>言復位者明始/降時位在此</span>主人坐取爵沃洗者西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1515:1546'>北靣<span class='krp-note'>沃洗者主/人之羣吏</span>卒洗主人壹揖壹讓升<span class='krp-note'>俱升/古文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1546:1573'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-3b' );" name="004-3b" class="pb">[004-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1573:1602'><span class='krp-note'>一作/壹</span>賔拜洗主人坐奠爵遂拜降盥<span class='krp-note'>復盥爲/手坋汙</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1602:1621'>賔降主人辭賔對復位當西序卒盥揖讓升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1621:1652'>賔西階上疑立<span class='krp-note'>疑讀爲疑然從於趙盾/之疑疑正立自定之皃</span>主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1652:1677'>坐取爵實之賔之席前西北靣獻賔<span class='krp-note'>獻進也/進酒於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1677:1703'><span class='krp-note'>賔</span>賔西階上拜主人少退<span class='krp-note'>少退/少辟</span>賔進受爵以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1703:1728'>復位主人阼階上拜送爵賔少退<span class='krp-note'>復位復西/階上位</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1728:1761'>薦脯醢<span class='krp-note'>薦進也進之/者主人有司</span>賔升席自西方<span class='krp-note'>升由下/也升必</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1761:1791'><span class='krp-note'>中/席</span>乃設折俎<span class='krp-note'>牲體枝解/節折在俎</span>主人阼階東疑立賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1791:1818'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-4a' );" name="004-4a" class="pb">[004-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1818:1845'>坐左執爵祭脯醢<span class='krp-note'>坐坐於席祭脯/醢者以右手</span>奠爵于薦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1845:1864'>西興右手取肺卻左手執本坐弗繚右絶末</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1864:1892'>以祭尚左手嚌之興加于俎<span class='krp-note'>興起也肺離之/本端厚大者繚</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1892:1928'><span class='krp-note'>猶紾也大夫以上威儀多紾絶之尚/左手者明垂紾之乃絶其末嚌甞也</span>坐挩手</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1928:1959'>遂祭酒<span class='krp-note'>挩拭也古/文挩作說</span>興席末坐啐酒<span class='krp-note'>啐亦/甞也</span>降席</span><br/>
