<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2007:2035'>拜執爵興主人阼階上荅拜<span class='krp-note'>卒盡也於此盡/酒者明此席非</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2035:2062'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-4b' );" name="004-4b" class="pb">[004-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2062:2100'><span class='krp-note'>專爲飮/食起</span>賔降洗<span class='krp-note'>將酢/主人</span>主人降<span class='krp-note'>亦從賔也降降/立阼階東西靣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2100:2124'>賔坐奠爵興辭<span class='krp-note'>西階/前也</span>主人對賔坐取爵適洗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2124:2143'>南北靣主人阼階東南靣辭洗賔坐奠爵于</span><br/>
