<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2265:2292'>北方設折俎祭如賔禮<span class='krp-note'>祭者祭薦俎/及酒亦嚌啐</span>不告旨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2292:2316'><span class='krp-note'>酒巳/物也</span>自席前適阼階上北靣坐卒爵興坐奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2316:2343'>爵遂拜執爵興賔西階上荅拜<span class='krp-note'>自席前者啐/酒席末因從</span></span><br/>
