<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2870:2889'>立于西階東薦脯醢介升席自北方設折俎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2889:2916'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-6b' );" name="004-6b" class="pb">[004-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2916:2935'>祭如賔禮不嚌肺不啐酒不告旨自南方降</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2935:2954'>席北靣坐卒爵興坐奠爵遂拜執爵興主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2954:2978'>介右荅拜<span class='krp-note'>不嚌啐/下賔</span>介降洗主人復阼階降辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2978:3008'>如初<span class='krp-note'>如賔酢/之時</span>卒洗主人盥<span class='krp-note'>盥者當/爲介酌</span>介揖讓升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3008:3038'>授主人爵于兩楹之間<span class='krp-note'>就尊南授之介不自/酌下賔酒者賔主共</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3038:3059'><span class='krp-note'>之</span>介西階上立主人實爵酢于西階上介右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3059:3078'>坐奠爵遂拜執爵興介荅拜主人坐祭遂飮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3078:3097'>卒爵興坐奠爵遂拜執爵興介荅拜主人坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3097:3124'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-7a' );" name="004-7a" class="pb">[004-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3124:3148'>奠爵于西楹南介右再拜崇酒介荅拜<span class='krp-note'>奠爵/西楹</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3148:3173'><span class='krp-note'>南以當/獻衆賔</span>主人復阼階揖降介降立于賔南主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3173:3198'>人西南靣三拜衆賔衆賔皆荅壹拜<span class='krp-note'>三拜壹/拜示徧</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3198:3224'><span class='krp-note'>不備禮也不/升拜賤也</span>主人揖升坐取爵于西楹下降</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3224:3243'>洗升實爵于西階上獻衆賔衆賔之長升拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3243:3276'>受者三人<span class='krp-note'>長其老者言三/人則衆賔多矣</span>主人拜送<span class='krp-note'>於衆/賔右</span>坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3276:3301'>祭立飲不拜旣爵授主人爵降復位<span class='krp-note'>旣卒也/卒爵不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3301:3327'><span class='krp-note'>拜立飮立授/賤者禮簡</span>衆賔獻則不拜受爵坐祭立飮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3327:3354'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-7b' );" name="004-7b" class="pb">[004-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3354:3386'><span class='krp-note'>次三人以下也/不拜禮彌簡</span>每一人獻則薦諸其席<span class='krp-note'>謂三/人也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3386:3416'>衆賔辯有脯醢<span class='krp-note'>亦每獻薦於其位位/在下今文辯皆作徧</span>主人以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='3416:3440'>爵降奠于篚<span class='krp-note'>不復/用也</span>揖讓升賔厭介升介厭衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='3440:3468'>賔升衆賔序升即席<span class='krp-note'>序次也即就也/今文厭皆爲揖</span>一人洗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='3468:3495'>升舉觶于賔<span class='krp-note'>一人主人之吏/發酒端曰舉</span>實觶西階上坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='3495:3514'>奠觶遂拜執觶興賔席末荅拜坐祭遂飮卒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='3514:3533'>觶興坐奠觶遂拜執觶興賔荅拜降洗升實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='3533:3558'>觶立于西階上賔拜<span class='krp-note'>賔拜拜/將受觶</span>進坐奠觶于薦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='3558:3585'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-8a' );" name="004-8a" class="pb">[004-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='3585:3617'>西賔辭坐受以興<span class='krp-note'>舉觶不授下主人也言坐/受者明行事相接若親受</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3617:3644'><span class='krp-note'>謙/也</span>舉觶者西階上拜送賔坐奠觶于其所<span class='krp-note'>所/薦</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3644:3678'><span class='krp-note'>西/也</span>舉觶者降<span class='krp-note'>事/巳</span>設席于堂廉東上<span class='krp-note'>爲工布席/也側邊曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3678:3717'><span class='krp-note'>廉燕禮曰席工於西階上少東樂正先升北/靣此言樂正先升立于西階東則工席在階</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3717:3738'><span class='krp-note'>東</span>工四人二瑟瑟先相者二人皆左何瑟後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3738:3769'>首挎越内弦右手相<span class='krp-note'>四人大夫制也二瑟二/人鼔瑟則二人歌也瑟</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3769:3809'><span class='krp-note'>先者將入序在前也相扶工也衆賔之少者/爲之毎工一人鄕射禮曰弟子相工如𥘉入</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3809:3848'><span class='krp-note'>天子相工使視瞭者凡工瞽矇也故有扶之/者師冕見及階子曰階也及席子曰席也固</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3848:3875'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-8b' );" name="004-8b" class="pb">[004-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3875:3914'><span class='krp-note'>相師之道後首者變于君也挎持也相瑟者/則爲之持瑟其相歌者徒相也越瑟下孔也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3914:3943'><span class='krp-note'>内弦側/擔之者</span>樂正先升立于西階東<span class='krp-note'>正長/也</span>工入升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3943:3966'>自西階北靣坐相者東靣坐遂授瑟乃降<span class='krp-note'>降/立</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3966:3998'><span class='krp-note'>于西方/近其事</span>工歌鹿鳴四牡皇皇者華<span class='krp-note'>三者皆小/雅篇也鹿</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3998:4037'><span class='krp-note'>鳴君與臣下及四方之賔燕講道修政之樂/歌也此采其巳有旨酒以召嘉賔嘉賔旣來</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='4037:4076'><span class='krp-note'>示我以善道又樂嘉賔有孔昭之明德可則/傚也四牡君勞使臣之來樂歌也此采其勤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4076:4115'><span class='krp-note'>苦王事念將父母懷歸傷悲忠孝之至以勞/賔也皇皇者華君遣使臣之樂歌也此采其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4115:4147'><span class='krp-note'>更是勞苦自以爲不及欲諮/謀于賢知而以自光明也</span>卒歌主人獻工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4147:4174'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-9a' );" name="004-9a" class="pb">[004-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4174:4193'>工左瑟一人拜不興受爵主人阼階上拜送</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4193:4226'>爵<span class='krp-note'>一人工之長也凢/工賤不爲之洗</span>薦脯醢使人相祭<span class='krp-note'>使人/相者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='4226:4255'><span class='krp-note'>相其祭/酒祭薦</span>工飮不拜旣爵授主人爵<span class='krp-note'>坐授/之</span>衆工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='4255:4281'>則不拜受爵祭飮辯有脯醢不祭<span class='krp-note'>祭飮獻酒/重無不祭</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='4281:4306'><span class='krp-note'>也今文/辯爲徧</span>大師則爲之洗賔介降主人辭降工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='4306:4342'>不辭洗<span class='krp-note'>大夫若君賜之樂謂之大師則爲之/洗尊之也賔介降從主人也工大師</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='4342:4378'><span class='krp-note'>也上旣言獻工矣乃言太師者大師/或瑟或歌也其獻之瑟則先歌則後</span>笙入堂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='4378:4404'>下磬南北靣立樂南陔白華華黍<span class='krp-note'>笙吹笙者/也以笙吹</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='4404:4431'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-9b' );" name="004-9b" class="pb">[004-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='4431:4470'><span class='krp-note'>此詩以爲樂也南陔白華華黍小雅篇也今/亡其義未聞昔周之興也周公制禮作樂采</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='4470:4509'><span class='krp-note'>時世之詩以爲樂歌所以通情相風切也其/有此篇明矣後世衰微幽厲尤甚禮樂之書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='4509:4548'><span class='krp-note'>稍稍廢棄孔子曰吾自衛反魯然後樂正唯/頌各得其所謂當時在者而復重雜亂者也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='4548:4587'><span class='krp-note'>惡能存其亡者乎且正考父校商之名頌十/二篇于周大師歸以祀其先王至孔子二百</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='4587:4614'><span class='krp-note'>年之間五篇而/巳此其信也</span>主人獻之于西階上一人拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='4614:4633'>盡階不升堂受爵主人拜送爵階前坐祭立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='4633:4662'>飮不拜旣爵升授主人爵<span class='krp-note'>一人笙之長者也/笙三人和一人凢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='4662:4690'><span class='krp-note'>四人鄕射禮曰/笙一人拜于下</span>衆笙則不拜受爵坐祭立飮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='4690:4718'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-10a' );" name="004-10a" class="pb">[004-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='4718:4750'>辯有脯醢不祭<span class='krp-note'>亦受爵于西階上薦之皆/於其位磬南今文辯爲徧</span>乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='4750:4769'>閒歌魚麗笙由庚歌南有嘉魚笙崇丘歌南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='4769:4802'>山有臺笙由儀<span class='krp-note'>閒代也謂一歌則一吹六者/皆小雅篇也魚麗言太平年</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='4802:4841'><span class='krp-note'>豐物多也此采其物多酒旨所以優賔也南/有嘉魚言太平君子有酒樂與賢者共之也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='4841:4880'><span class='krp-note'>此采其能以禮下賢者賢者纍蔓而歸之與/之燕樂也南山有臺言太平之治以賢者爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='4880:4919'><span class='krp-note'>本此采其愛友賢者爲邦家之基民之父母/旣欲其身之壽考又欲其名德之長也由庚</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='4919:4946'><span class='krp-note'>崇丘由儀今/亡其義未聞</span>乃合樂周南關雎葛覃卷耳召</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='4946:4978'>南鵲巢采蘩采蘋<span class='krp-note'>合樂謂歌樂與衆聲俱作/周南召南國風篇也王后</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='4978:5006'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-10b' );" name="004-10b" class="pb">[004-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='5006:5045'><span class='krp-note'>國君夫人房中之樂歌也關雎言后妃之德/葛覃言后妃之職卷耳言后妃之志鵲巢言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='5045:5084'><span class='krp-note'>國君夫人之德采蘩言國君夫人不失職采/蘋言卿大夫之妻能脩其法度昔大王王季</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='5084:5123'><span class='krp-note'>居于岐山之陽躬行召南之教以興王業及/文王而行周南之教以受命大雅云刑于寡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='5123:5162'><span class='krp-note'>妻至于兄弟以御于家邦謂此也其始一國/耳文王作邑于豐以故地爲卿士之采地乃</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='5162:5203'><span class='krp-note'>分爲二國周周公罰所食召召公所食於時文/王三分天下有其巳一德化被于南土是以其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='5203:5242'><span class='krp-note'>詩有仁賢之風者屬之召南焉有聖人之風/者屬之周南焉夫婦之道生民之本王政之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='5242:5281'><span class='krp-note'>端此六篇者其教之原也故國君與其臣下/及四方之賔燕用之合樂也鄕樂者風也小</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='5281:5320'><span class='krp-note'>雅爲諸侯之樂大雅頌爲天子之樂鄕飮酒/升歌小雅禮盛者可以進取也燕合鄕樂禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='5320:5348'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-11a' );" name="004-11a" class="pb">[004-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='5348:5387'><span class='krp-note'>輕者可以逮下也春秋傳曰肆夏繫遏渠天/子所以享元侯也文王大明緜兩君相見之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='5387:5426'><span class='krp-note'>樂也然則諸侯相與燕升歌大雅合小雅天/子與次國小國之君燕亦如之與大國之君</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='5426:5455'><span class='krp-note'>燕升歌頌合大雅/其笙間之篇未聞</span>工告于樂正曰正歌備樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='5455:5486'>正告于賔乃降<span class='krp-note'>樂正降者以正歌備無/事也降立西階東北靣</span>主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='5486:5516'>降席自南方<span class='krp-note'>不由北/方由便</span>側降<span class='krp-note'>賔介/不從</span>作相爲司正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='5516:5542'>司正禮辭許諾主人拜司正荅拜<span class='krp-note'>作使也禮/樂之正旣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='5542:5573'><span class='krp-note'>成將留賔爲有解惰立/司正以監之拜拜其許</span>主人升復席司正洗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='5573:5592'>觶升自西階阼階上北靣受命于主人主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='5592:5620'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-11b' );" name="004-11b" class="pb">[004-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='5620:5645'>曰請安于賔司正告于賔賔禮辭許<span class='krp-note'>爲賔欲/去留之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='5645:5669'><span class='krp-note'>告賔於/西階</span>司正告于主人主人阼階上再拜賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='5669:5688'>西階上荅拜司正立于楹間以相拜皆揖復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='5688:5725'>席<span class='krp-note'>再拜拜賔許也司正旣以賔許告主人/遂立楹間以相拜賔王人旣拜揖就席</span>司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='5725:5744'>正實觶降自西階階間北靣坐奠觶退共少</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='5744:5782'>立<span class='krp-note'>階間北靣東西節也其南北當中庭共拱/手也少立自正愼其位也巳帥而正孰敢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='5782:5808'><span class='krp-note'>不正燕禮曰/右還北靣</span>坐取觶不祭遂飲卒觶興坐奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='5808:5827'>觶遂拜執觶興盥洗北靣坐奠觶于其所退</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='5827:5855'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-12a' );" name="004-12a" class="pb">[004-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='5855:5884'>立于觶南<span class='krp-note'>洗觶奠之示潔敬/立於其南以察衆</span>賔北面坐取俎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='5884:5903'>西之觶阼階上北面酬主人主人降席立于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='5903:5937'>賔東<span class='krp-note'>初起旅酬也凡旅酬者少長以齒/終於沃盥者皆弟長而無遺矣</span>賔坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='5937:5956'>奠觶遂拜執觶興主人荅拜不祭立飮不拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='5956:5983'>卒觶不洗實觶東南面授主人<span class='krp-note'>賔立飮卒觶/因更酌以鄕</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='5983:6007'><span class='krp-note'>主人/將授</span>主人阼階上拜賔少退主人受觶賔拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='6007:6037'>送于主人之西<span class='krp-note'>旅酬同/階禮殺</span>賔揖復席<span class='krp-note'>酬主/人訖</span>主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='6037:6056'>西階上酬介介降席自南方立于主人之西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='6056:6084'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-12b' );" name="004-12b" class="pb">[004-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='6084:6111'>如賔酬主人之禮主人揖復席<span class='krp-note'>其酌實觶西/南面授介自</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='6111:6138'><span class='krp-note'>此以下旅酬/酌者亦如之</span>司正升相旅曰某子受酬一酬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='6138:6174'>者降席<span class='krp-note'>旅序也於是介酬衆賔衆賔又以次/序相酬某者衆賔姓也同姓則以伯</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='6174:6206'><span class='krp-note'>仲别之又同則/以且字别之</span>司正退立于序端東面<span class='krp-note'>辟受/酬者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='6206:6242'><span class='krp-note'>又便其賛上賛下也/始升相西階西北面</span>受酬者自介右<span class='krp-note'>由介東/也尊介</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='6242:6276'><span class='krp-note'>使不失/故位</span>衆受酬者受自左<span class='krp-note'>後將受酬者皆由/西變於介也今文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='6276:6306'><span class='krp-note'>無衆/酬者</span>拜興飮皆如賔酬主人之禮<span class='krp-note'>嫌賔以/下異也</span>辯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='6306:6335'>卒受者以觶降坐奠于篚<span class='krp-note'>辯辯衆賔之在下/者鄕射禮曰辯遂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='6335:6363'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-13a' );" name="004-13a" class="pb">[004-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='6363:6396'><span class='krp-note'>酬在下者皆升/受酬于西階上</span>司正降復位<span class='krp-note'>觶南/之位</span>使二人舉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='6396:6415'>觶于賔介洗升實觶于西階上皆坐奠觶遂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='6415:6434'>拜執觶興賔介席末荅拜皆坐祭遂飮卒觶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='6434:6458'>興坐奠觶遂拜執觶興賔介席末荅拜<span class='krp-note'>二人/亦主</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='6458:6496'><span class='krp-note'>人之吏若有大夫則舉觶于賔與大夫燕禮/曰媵爵者立于洗南西靣北上序進盥洗</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='6496:6519'>逆降洗升實觶皆立于西階上賔介皆拜<span class='krp-note'>於/席</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='6519:6542'><span class='krp-note'>末/拜</span>皆進薦西奠之賔辭坐取觶以興介則薦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='6542:6561'>南奠之介坐受以興退皆拜送降賔介奠于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='6561:6589'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-13b' );" name="004-13b" class="pb">[004-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='6589:6618'>其所<span class='krp-note'>賔言取介言受尊卑/異文今文曰賔受</span>司正升自西階受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='6618:6642'>命于主人主人曰請坐于賔賔辭以俎<span class='krp-note'>至此/盛禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='6642:6681'><span class='krp-note'>俱成酒清肴乾賔主百拜強有力者猶倦焉/張而不弛弛而不張非文武之道請坐者將</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='6681:6713'><span class='krp-note'>以賔燕也俎者肴之貴者辭/之者不敢以禮殺當貴者</span>主人請徹俎賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='6713:6742'>許<span class='krp-note'>亦司正傳/請告之</span>司正降階前命弟子俟徹俎<span class='krp-note'>西/階</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='6742:6778'><span class='krp-note'>前也弟子賔之少者俎者主人之吏/設之使弟子俟徹者明徹俎賔之義</span>司正升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='6778:6801'>立于席端<span class='krp-note'>待/事</span>賔降席北面主人降席阼階上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='6801:6820'>北面介降席西階上北面遵者降席席東南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='6820:6848'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-14a' );" name="004-14a" class="pb">[004-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='6848:6886'>靣<span class='krp-note'>皆立相須徹俎也遵者謂此鄕之人仕至/大夫者也今來助主人樂賔主人所榮而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='6886:6921'><span class='krp-note'>遵法者也因以爲名或有無來不/來用時事耳今文遵爲僎或爲全</span>賔取俎還</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='6921:6940'>授司正司正以降賔從之主人取俎還授弟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='6940:6959'>子弟子以降自西階主人降自阼階介取俎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='6959:6978'>還授弟子弟子以降介從之若有諸公大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='6978:7005'>則使人受俎如賔禮衆賔皆降<span class='krp-note'>取俎者皆鄕/其席旣授弟</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='7005:7040'><span class='krp-note'>子皆降復/𥘉入之位</span>說屨揖讓如初升坐<span class='krp-note'>說屨者爲安/燕當坐也必</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='7040:7080'><span class='krp-note'>說於下者屨賤不空居堂說屨/主人先左賔先右今文說爲稅</span>乃羞<span class='krp-note'>羞進也/所進者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='7080:7108'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-14b' );" name="004-14b" class="pb">[004-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='7108:7145'><span class='krp-note'>狗胾醢也鄕設骨體所以致敬也今進/羞所以盡愛也敬之愛之所以厚賢也</span>無筭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='7145:7183'>爵<span class='krp-note'>筭數也賔主燕飮爵行無數醉而止也鄕/射禮曰使二人舉觶于賔與大夫又曰執</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='7183:7221'><span class='krp-note'>觶者洗升實觶反奠/於賔與大夫皆是</span>無筭樂<span class='krp-note'>燕樂亦無數或/間或合盡歡而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='7221:7256'><span class='krp-note'>止也春秋襄二十九年吳公子札/來聘請觀于周樂此國君之無筭</span>賔出奏陔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='7256:7295'><span class='krp-note'>陔陔夏也陔之言戒也終日燕飮酒罷以陔/爲節明無失禮也周禮鍾師以鍾鼓奏九夏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='7295:7334'><span class='krp-note'>是奏陔夏則有鍾鼓矣鍾鼔者天子諸侯備/用之大夫士鼔而巳蓋建於阼階之西南鼔</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='7334:7367'><span class='krp-note'>鄕射禮曰賔興樂正命奏陔賔/降及階陔作賔出衆賔皆出</span>主人送于門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='7367:7396'>外再拜<span class='krp-note'>門東西靣拜也賔介/不荅拜禮有終也</span>賔若有遵者諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='7396:7424'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-15a' );" name="004-15a" class="pb">[004-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='7424:7452'>公大夫則旣一人舉觶乃入<span class='krp-note'>不于主人正禮/也遵者諸公大</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='7452:7484'><span class='krp-note'>夫也謂之賔者同從外來/耳大國有孤四命謂之公</span>席于賔東公三重</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='7484:7519'>大夫再重<span class='krp-note'>席此二者於賔東尊之不與鄕人/齒也天子之國三命者不齒於諸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='7519:7551'><span class='krp-note'>侯之國爵爲大夫則不齒矣/不言遵者遵者亦卿大夫</span>公如大夫入主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='7551:7570'>人降賔介降衆賔皆降復初位主人迎揖讓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='7570:7595'>升公升如賔禮辭一席使一人去之<span class='krp-note'>如讀若/今之若</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='7595:7625'><span class='krp-note'>主人迎之於門内也辭/一席謙自同於大夫</span>大夫則如介禮有諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='7625:7644'>公則辭加席委于席端主人不徹無諸公則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='7644:7672'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-15b' );" name="004-15b" class="pb">[004-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='7672:7699'>大夫辭加席主人對不去加席<span class='krp-note'>加席上席也/大夫席再重</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='7699:7729'>明日賔服鄕服以拜賜<span class='krp-note'>拜賜謝恩惠鄕服昨/日與鄉大夫飮酒之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='7729:7760'><span class='krp-note'>朝服也不言朝服未服以/朝也今文曰賔服鄕服</span>主人如賔服以拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='7760:7798'>辱<span class='krp-note'>拜賔復自屈辱也鄕射禮曰賔朝服以拜/賜于門外主人不見如賔服遂從之拜辱</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='7798:7831'><span class='krp-note'>于門外/乃退</span>主人釋服<span class='krp-note'>釋朝服更服玄端/也古文釋作舍</span>乃息司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='7831:7870'>正<span class='krp-note'>息勞也勞賜昨日賛執事/者獨云司正司正庭長也</span>無介<span class='krp-note'>勞禮略也/司正爲賔</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='7870:7902'>不殺<span class='krp-note'>市買若因所有可/也不殺則無俎</span>薦脯醢<span class='krp-note'>羞同/也</span>羞唯所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='7902:7930'>有<span class='krp-note'>在有/何物</span>徴唯所欲<span class='krp-note'>徴召/也</span>以吿于先生君子可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='7930:7958'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-16a' );" name="004-16a" class="pb">[004-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='7958:7996'>也<span class='krp-note'>告請也先生不以筋力爲禮於是可以來/君子國中有盛德者可者召不召唯所欲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='7996:8029'>賔介不與<span class='krp-note'>禮瀆則䙝古/文與爲豫</span>鄕樂唯欲<span class='krp-note'>鄕樂周南/召南六篇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='8029:8061'><span class='krp-note'>之中唯所欲作不從次也不/歌鹿鳴魚麗者辟國君也</span>記鄕朝服而謀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='8061:8092'>賔介皆使能不宿戒<span class='krp-note'>鄕鄕人謂鄕大夫也朝/服冠玄端緇帶素韠白</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='8092:8131'><span class='krp-note'>屨今郡國行鄕飮酒之禮玄冠而衣皮弁服/與禮異再戒爲宿戒禮將有事先戒而又宿</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='8131:8162'><span class='krp-note'>戒</span>蒲筵緇布純<span class='krp-note'>筵席也/純縁也</span>尊綌幂賔至徹之<span class='krp-note'>綌/葛</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='8162:8197'><span class='krp-note'>也幂覆/尊巾</span>其牲狗也<span class='krp-note'>狗取/擇人</span>亨于堂東北<span class='krp-note'>祖陽氣/之所始</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='8197:8229'><span class='krp-note'>也陽氣主養易曰天地養/萬物聖人養賢以及萬民</span>獻用爵其他用觶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='8229:8257'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-16b' );" name="004-16b" class="pb">[004-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='8257:8286'><span class='krp-note'>爵尊不/䙝用之</span>薦脯五挺橫祭于其上出自左房<span class='krp-note'>挺/猶</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='8286:8325'><span class='krp-note'>膱也鄕射禮曰祭半膱膱長尺有二寸左在/東陽也陽主養房饌陳處也冠禮之饌脯醢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='8325:8359'><span class='krp-note'>南上曲禮曰以脯/修置者左朐右末</span>俎由東壁自西階升<span class='krp-note'>亨狗/旣孰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='8359:8384'><span class='krp-note'>載之俎饌/於東方</span>賔俎脊脅肩肺主人俎脊脅臂肺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='8384:8408'>介俎脊脅肫胳肺肺皆離皆右體進腠<span class='krp-note'>凡牲/前脛</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='8408:8447'><span class='krp-note'>骨三肩臂臑也後脛骨二膊胳也尊者俎尊/骨卑者俎卑骨祭統曰凡爲俎者以骨爲主</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='8447:8490'><span class='krp-note'>骨有貴賤凡前貴後賤離猶㨒也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR3370' title='KR3370' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR3370.png'/>/理也進理謂前其本也今文胳作骼</span>以爵拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='8490:8520'>者不徒作<span class='krp-note'>作起也言拜旣爵者/不徒起起必酢主人</span>坐卒爵者拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='8520:8548'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-17a' );" name="004-17a" class="pb">[004-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='8548:8577'>旣爵立卒爵者不拜旣爵<span class='krp-note'>降殺各從其宜不/使相錯唯工不從</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='8577:8610'><span class='krp-note'>此/禮</span>凡奠者於左<span class='krp-note'>不飲者不/欲其妨</span>將舉於右<span class='krp-note'>便/也</span>衆賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='8610:8640'>之長一人辭洗如賔禮<span class='krp-note'>於三人之中復差有/尊者餘二人雖爲之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='8640:8666'><span class='krp-note'>洗不敢辭/其下不洗</span>立者東靣北上若有北靣者則東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='8666:8695'>上<span class='krp-note'>賢者衆寡無常也或/統於堂或統於門</span>樂正與立者皆薦以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='8695:8733'>齒<span class='krp-note'>謂其飮之次也尊樂正同於賔黨不言飮/而言薦以明飮也旣飮皆薦於其位樂正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='8733:8766'><span class='krp-note'>位西階/東北靣</span>凡舉爵三作而不徒爵<span class='krp-note'>謂獻賔獻大/夫獻工皆有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='8766:8792'><span class='krp-note'>薦</span>樂作大夫不入<span class='krp-note'>後樂/賢者</span>獻工與笙取爵于上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='8792:8820'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-17b' );" name="004-17b" class="pb">[004-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='8820:8851'>篚旣獻奠于下篚<span class='krp-note'>明其異器敬也如是則/獻大夫亦然上篚三爵</span>其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='8851:8883'>笙則獻諸西階上<span class='krp-note'>謂主人拜送爵也於工拜/于阼階上者以其坐于西</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='8883:8922'><span class='krp-note'>階東也古/文無上</span>磬階間縮<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0764' title='KR0764' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0764.png'/>北靣鼔之<span class='krp-note'>縮從也霫/以東西爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='8922:8959'><span class='krp-note'>從鼔猶擊也大夫而特縣方賔鄕人之賢/者從士禮也射則磬在東古文縮爲蹙</span>主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='8959:8986'>人介凡升席自北方降自南方<span class='krp-note'>席南上升由/下降由上由</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='8986:9016'><span class='krp-note'>便</span>司正旣舉觶而薦諸其位<span class='krp-note'>司正主人之屬/也無獻因其舉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='9016:9050'><span class='krp-note'>觶而/薦之</span>凡旅不洗<span class='krp-note'>敬禮/殺也</span>不洗者不祭<span class='krp-note'>不甚/絜也</span>旣旅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='9050:9077'>士不入<span class='krp-note'>後正禮也旣/旅則將燕矣</span>徹俎賔介遵者之俎受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='9077:9105'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '004-18a' );" name="004-18a" class="pb">[004-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='9105:9132'>者以降遂出授從者<span class='krp-note'>以送/之</span>主人之俎以東<span class='krp-note'>藏/於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='9132:9155'><span class='krp-note'>東/方</span>樂正命奏陔賔出至于階陔作若有諸公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='9155:9181'>則大夫於主人之北西靣<span class='krp-note'>其西靣者北/上統於公</span>主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='9181:9211'>之賛者西靣北上不與<span class='krp-note'>賛佐也謂主人之屬/佐助主人禮事微鼏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='9211:9244'><span class='krp-note'>沃盥設薦俎者西靣北上統於/堂也與及也不及謂不獻酒</span>無筭爵然後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='9244:9254'>與<span class='krp-note'>燕乃/及之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='9254:9261'>儀禮卷第四</span><br/>
